flow.description: This flow list the updated file from the cloud and fetch the data from the updated file and load to the PostgreSQL database
flow.name: cloud-database-el

source.comments: Get the file from the SFTP server
source.name: GetSFTP

controllerServices.comments: This is controller services is used to fetch the files from the Azure Blob Storage
controllerServices.name: ListBlob-RawWindData

properties.schema-text:
{
  "type": "record",
  "name": "WeatherRecord",
  "fields": [
    { "name": "DATE", "type": "string" },
    { "name": "WIND", "type": ["null", "double"], "default": null },
    { "name": "IND", "type": ["null", "int"], "default": null },
    { "name": "RAIN", "type": ["null", "double"], "default": null },
    { "name": "IND_1", "type": ["null", "int"], "default": null },
    { "name": "T_MAX", "type": ["null", "double"], "default": null },
    { "name": "IND_2", "type": ["null", "int"], "default": null },
    { "name": "T_MIN", "type": ["null", "double"], "default": null },
    { "name": "T_MIN_G", "type": ["null", "double"], "default": null }
  ]
}
